# Critical Environment Variables - Add These to Your .env File

## Database Configuration
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/nexusai

## Authentication & Security
SECRET_KEY=your-very-secret-key-replace-me
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=480  # 8 hours - standard enterprise session timeout

## Billing Configuration
REQUEST_COST_PER_1K_TOKENS=0.002

## Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_PER_MIN=120

## LLM API Keys (Choose at least one for optimal performance)

### Gemini API (RECOMMENDED - Best for long-form responses)
# Get your key from: https://ai.google.dev
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here

### Groq API (Fast fallback - High-speed mode)
# Get your key from: https://console.groq.com
GROQ_API_KEY=your-groq-api-key-here

### Ollama (Local fallback - No API key needed)
OLLAMA_URL=http://localhost:11434/api/generate
OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3

## Stripe Integration (Optional - for production billing)
STRIPE_API_KEY=your-stripe-secret-key
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your-webhook-secret

---

## Session Timeout Notes:
- Changed from 24 hours (1440 minutes) to 8 hours (480 minutes)
- This is the industry standard for enterprise applications
- Users will need to re-login after 8 hours of inactivity
- To increase further, set ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES to desired value in minutes
